                <img src="images/web-development.jpg" alt="post Image" class="post-img">
                <h2 class="post-title">Starting My Journey in web Development</h2>
                <p class="post-date">Posted on October 6, 2025 by Hassan Mohamed</p>

                <p>
                    Learning web development has been one of the most rewarding experiences of my life.
                    I started with a simple HTML and CSS projects and slowly built my way up to full websites.
                    It wasn't easy, but consistency and curiosty made all the difference.
                </p>

                <p>
                    What really helped is breaking down every small concept ــ Understanding how each tag, and property worked,
                    I learned that the best way to grow is building real projects, on step at a time.
                </p>

                <p>
                    My advice to beginners: Don't rush, celebrate small wins, stay curious, and always keep expirementing,
                    every line of code you write is a step forward.
                </p>

